HEADWORD: Strout
<hw>Strout</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Strut</er>.]</ety> <def>To swell; to puff out; to project.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

