==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Strout
<hw>Strout</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cause to project or swell out;
to enlarge affectedly; to strut.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

